four of them.

11:34.151 --> 11:35.250
What?

11:35.399 --> 11:37.503
Jesus, Helen, nice work.

11:39.086 --> 11:43.628
Yeah, I don't see too much
of them, but I try.

11:44.204 --> 11:46.750
Did you ever remarry?

11:49.774 --> 11:51.332
Yeah, I did.

11:51.688 --> 11:53.016
Oh?

11:53.119 --> 11:54.546
Tell me about her.

11:54.682 --> 11:56.525
Well, she's, uh...

11:58.704 --> 12:00.596
She's dead.

12:01.030 --> 12:02.196
