big-time author.

13:31.107 --> 13:33.916
He was there because
he wanted to be.

13:34.162 --> 13:36.711
Because he cared
so much about us.

13:36.833 --> 13:39.273
Because he was
a good man.

13:40.193 --> 13:43.465
He'd wave George Orwell around
like they were peers

13:43.542 --> 13:44.887
and weep over Eliot.

13:44.964 --> 13:47.074
