14:11.576 --> 14:13.583
He believes in my future.

14:14.779 --> 14:16.742
Also, he's fucking my mother.

14:18.396 --> 14:21.207
But that doesn't matter,
because he cares.

14:21.334 --> 14:22.991
Look how he parts the seas

14:23.068 --> 14:26.258
for a boy like me
to walk right into Canaan.

14:26.607 --> 14:28.481
He's got kids
of his own, you know.

14:28.558 --> 14:30.477
